# Override the global ~/.npmrc's @cloudflare scope redirect.
#
# The global config points @cloudflare to a private gateway
# (registry-gateway.cloudflare-ui.workers.dev) which returns HTML for
# unauthenticated requests and breaks `bun install`. The @cloudflare
# packages we consume (vite-plugin, workers-types, etc.) are all published
# to the public npm registry, so we pin the scope back to it here.
@cloudflare:registry=https://registry.npmjs.org/
